# VHS tape template — render with: vhs demo.tape
# Docs: https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs
# dustjacket fills the Type lines with the repo's real commands; you run the render.

Output docs/assets/demo.gif

Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1200
Set Height 600
Set Padding 20
Set Theme "Dracula"

# --- replace the lines below with real commands from the repo ---
Type "mytool --help"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "mytool run example"
Enter
Sleep 4s
